This project is a mobile-first apartment cleaning routine app. Build for small screens first. Use TypeScript, React, Next.js App Router, and Tailwind CSS. Keep the first release no-login and local-first with localStorage. Public templates are public. Personal progress is private. Do not add authentication, databases, Google sync, payments, or external services unless explicitly requested. Use accessible HTML controls. Keep components small. Keep copy original. Do not copy FlyLady branding, protected phrases, paid content, app screens, icons, or assets. After each feature, run lint and build, then explain what changed.
